frames.caption: A group of people stand in awe before a colossal stone figure towering over the pyramids. The scene is set in a desert landscape with a mystical atmosphere, as the giant structure looms in the background. Dust swirls around the pyramids, adding to the surreal and ancient ambiance.
frames.description: The scene takes place in a desert setting, likely inspired by ancient Egypt, with pyramids prominently featured. A massive stone figure resembling a humanoid creature stands imposingly among the pyramids, capturing the attention of the people gathered in the foreground.

frames.caption: A colossal stone figure looms over an ancient pyramid, its massive form stirring up clouds of dust. Two small human figures are seen running across the sandy terrain, dwarfed by the monumental structure.
frames.description: The scene is set in a desert landscape, dominated by an ancient pyramid and a gigantic stone figure resembling a mythical creature. The atmosphere is tense and dramatic, with the movement of the giant causing dust to swirl around.

frames.caption: A massive stone-like creature is seen moving forward on all fours, creating a cloud of dust beneath it. The creature's surface is textured and rugged, resembling ancient rock formations.
frames.description: The scene depicts a giant, stone-like creature in a barren, dusty landscape. It appears to be in motion, suggesting a sense of power and ancient mystery.
